{
  "text": "Theorem 14 (Small odd solutions of NLKG, [CITATION_1] ). Assume that f is odd. There exists δ > 0 such that for any odd (u 0 , u 1 ) ∈ H 1 ×L 2 such that (u 0 , u 1 ) H 1 ×L 2 < δ, the global odd solution u of (16) with initial data (u 0 , u 1 ) satisfies, for any bounded interval I ⊂ R, Theorem 15 (Small solutions to NLKG with supercritical nonlinearity). Assume that for some C > 0, f satisfies, for all |u| < 1, ",
